QEMUCONF-IMPORT(1) General Commands Manual QEMUCONF-IMPORT(1)

NAME

qemuconf-import — make qemuconf file from currently running qemu instance

SYNOPSIS

qemuconf-import

DESCRIPTION

qemuconf-import creates configuration file for qemuconf(1) from currently running qemu(1) instance.

SEE ALSO

qemu(1), qemuconf(1)
